data.description: Great chance to own a 1 year old home. Exterior charm and covered front porch perfect for enjoying a fall afternoon.  Large open kitchen & great room with beautiful Luxury Vinyl Flooring. Stainless steel appliances with oversized island and granite countertops. The second story includes 3 Bedrooms & 2 Full Baths. Primary Bedroom has large walk-in closet and attached bathroom. Second story laundry making it so much easier.  Finished Basement adds loads of space. Great Location, Schools and neighborhood. Don't let this one slip away, schedule your tour today.
